OL,3,CAnalysis finds 'surprising'
OL,4,Cdestinations are cheapest for a summer
OL,5,Cbreak
OL,7,FMany of the cheapest European summer
OL,8,Fholidays available to book are in
OL,9,F"surprising" destinations, according
OL,10,Fto new analysis.
OL,12,FConsumer group Which? said its
OL,13,Fanalysis of more than 4,500 package
OL,14,Fholidays found the least expensive
OL,15,Fwere often in locations which people
OL,16,Fgenerally "assume to come with a
OL,17,Fhigher price tag", such as Italy's
OL,18,FAmalfi coast or Greek islands.
