OL,5,Cbreak
OL,7,FIt found that "traditionally low-cost
OL,8,Fdestinations like Bulgaria and Turkey"
OL,9,Fwere absent from the 10 cheapest
OL,10,Fholidays.
OL,12,FWhich? said this is partly because of
OL,13,Fthe type of packages available, with
OL,14,Fthe Amalfi coast have a wide choice of
OL,15,Faccommodation on either a self-
OL,16,Fcatering or bed and breakfast basis,
OL,17,Fwhich is usually cheaper than full
OL,18,Fboard packages.
OL,20,FThere are also lots of budget flights
OL,21,Fto the region.
