OL,3,CAnalysis finds 'surprising'
OL,4,Cdestinations are cheapest for a summer
OL,5,Cbreak
OL,7,FResearchers analysed seven-night
OL,8,Fholidays on sale for the first week of
OL,9,FAugust in 70 regions across 15
OL,10,FEuropean countries, finding that
OL,11,Fconsumers can save hundreds of pounds
OL,12,Fdepending on the destination they
OL,13,Fchoose.
OL,15,FThe cheapest average price was for
OL,16,Fbreaks on the tiny Greek island of
OL,17,FKalymnos, at #847.
